A man allegedly drove his Ford Ranger bakkie over an 18-month-old boy in Kameeldrift, Roodeplaat, on Monday. Police spokesperson Capt Mavela Masondo said the incident happened at about  5.30pm. “It is alleged that the driver of a Ford Ranger, who is one of the tenants at a block of rooms, was entering the yard when he ran over the child.” The boy was declared dead on the scene. A case of culpable homicide has been opened.